                "description": "Byte Kitchen is on a mission to bring America’s best restaurants to every neighborhood in the country through our novel operating model. We partner with stand-out restaurants and recreate their food for delivery in new markets, simultaneously expanding brand equity and consumer choice.\r\n\r\nByte Kitchen is backed by leading investors including Y-Combinator, Crosslink Capital, WndrCo, Soma Capital and strategic angels. We are a small and rapidly expanding team, and are seeking entrepreneurial individuals to join us.\r\n\r\nYour role:\r\n\r\nWe are seeking an Operations Intern to successfully manage and execute the many business functions that it takes to run a rapidly-growing company. This includes but is not limited to setting up financial and operating metrics for multiple parts of the business, kitchen ops, enhancing customer experience and building the operating playbook that enables the company to scale to multiple geographies.\r\n\r\nAs an early member of the team, you will have significant autonomy and will be involved in key day-to-day decision making. You will be exposed to every facet of the business, work with all team members and have the ability to define this role. If you are passionate about building the playbook that enables restaurant expansion at scale, this is the right role for you.\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n\r\nHigh work ethic\r\nExperience working in a fast-paced environment \r\nHighly organized, focused on metrics, immaculate attention to detail \r\nDeeply analytical using data to drive decision making \r\nExcellent problem solving and communication skills\r\n\r\nBonus:\r\n\r\nLove for food / restaurant industry \r\nStartup experience / experience in food delivery or logistics companies\r\n\r\nYou are:\r\n\r\nScrappy: you know when to prioritize speed over scalability and are comfortable making those decisions \r\n\r\nSelf-starter: there is no precedent, no playbook for how to do this; we have to create it together \r\n\r\nDelighted to take ownership: you alone decide the ceiling of the scope of your responsibilities\r\n\r\nWe are:\r\n\r\nCustomer obsessed: we serve two customers – our restaurant partners and the end consumers. Every decision we take is focused on improving experience for both \r\n\r\nHungry: to build a solution which is a true partnership for restaurants; to create the kitchen of the future; to bring the best food to our customers every day \r\n\r\nCollaborative: we have no time for office politics, everyone takes out the trash, all opinions are not only welcome but highly encouraged\r\n\r\n\r\nAt Byte Kitchen, we firmly believe there is only one way to build a sustainable business model in the food delivery industry – be a true partner to restaurants. We don’t pretend to have all the answers. But we do have an obsessive focus to figure them out and we want every single person’s input on the team to do so.\r\n\r\nIf you want to be part of a dynamic team that is transforming the way restaurants expand, please reach out to us at careers at bytekitchen.io",
