        "hiring_description":"At CareRev, we drive conversations that build the local, resilient, flexible healthcare workforce of the future. We're a technology platform empowering healthcare professionals to take control of their careers and provide a direct line between healthcare facilities and local clinical talent.\r\n\r\nBut our commitment to shifting the future of work extends beyond healthcare professionals. We lead with audacious goals and big ideas for growth, but we also prioritize healthy boundaries. The battle is best won together: we entrust individual team members to balance, grow, and achieve, and our organization is rewarded tenfold with grit, engagement, and boldness.\r\n\r\nWe're cultivating a more diverse, more equitable, more inclusive, and more accessible organizational culture. Join our talented CareRevolution team as we eliminate traditional barriers and friction within healthcare staffing.",
