              "interview_process":"Initial call with the CEO/CTO to learn more about the candidate's background, experience and motivation - and for candidate to learn more about the company. This would be a largely non-technical call. \r\n\r\nNext stage: technical interview with the CEO/CTO to identify candidate strengths and weaknesses with regards to specifics around powertrain and performance subject matter. \r\n\r\nThird stage: If promising you would be invited to chat to the rest of the team (on site or remotely) and present some prior project work, and we’ll do our best to show you why this is going to be a really, really impactful thing for you to do with your talent. If not attending on site we would do an additional step where you can meet the team in person and see our facilities. ",
